  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients hospitalized in internal medicine departments are given corticosteroid treatment
      according clinical indications. Patients receive treatment at different dosage levels and in
      different preparations according to clinical indications. This study will investigate how
      corticosteroids effect the heart and specifically, longitudinal strain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
