  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Change in Heart Function</measure>
    <time_frame>Two years</time_frame>
    <description>Heart contraction and specifically its longitudinal strain will be examined using Transthoracic Echocardiogram (TTE) before, during and after corticosteroid treatment. TTE reveals changes in contraction in the right and left ventricle and septum.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
